---
const links = [
  { href: "/news", label: "News" },
  { href: "/articles", label: "Articles" },
  { href: "/ideas", label: "Ideas" },
  { href: "/demos", label: "Demos" },
  { href: "/sim", label: "Simulation" },
];
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Build the Simulation</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="A living blueprint for building interactive simulations of neural systems — from peripheral nerve to cortex."
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main class="wrap">
      <header class="hero">
        <div class="brand">
          <div class="mark" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="titleblock">
            <h1>Build the Simulation</h1>
            <p class="sub">
              A living blueprint for simulating neural systems — and designing the interfaces that connect to them.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <nav class="nav">
          {links.map((l) => (
            <a class="pill" href={l.href}>{l.label}</a>
          ))}
        </nav>
      </header>

      <section class="card">
        <h2>What this is</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><b>Weekly signal:</b> curated BCI + neurotech news with commentary.</li>
          <li><b>Deep articles:</b> neuroscience → interfaces → fabrication → future systems.</li>
          <li><b>Interactive demos:</b> models and simulations you can manipulate in-browser.</li>
          <li><b>The sandbox:</b> a physics-based environment for exploring electrode designs and stimulation strategies.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="grid">
        <a class="tile" href="/news">
          <h3>News</h3>
          <p>Weekly BCI updates, startups, papers, and my take.</p>
        </a>

        <a class="tile" href="/articles">
          <h3>Articles</h3>
          <p>A guided sequence from fundamentals to future biohybrid interfaces.</p>
        </a>

        <a class="tile" href="/ideas">
          <h3>Ideas</h3>
          <p>Working notes, hypotheses, design sketches, and open questions.</p>
        </a>

        <a class="tile" href="/demos">
          <h3>Demos</h3>
          <p>Interactive models: fields, fibers, decoding, control, materials.</p>
        </a>

        <a class="tile" href="/sim">
          <h3>Simulation</h3>
          <p>The long-term sandbox: nerve + cortex cross-sections, implants, stimulation.</p>
        </a>

        <a class="tile" href="https://github.com/corbins-cryo-pod/buildthesimulation" target="_blank">
          <h3>Repository</h3>
          <p>Source code and roadmap.</p>
        </a>
      </section>

      <footer class="foot">
        <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} buildthesimulation.com</span>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :global(body) {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, "Apple Color Emoji",
      "Segoe UI Emoji";
    color: #0b0b10;
    background: radial-gradient(1000px 600px at 25% 10%, rgba(160, 120, 255, 0.18), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(800px 500px at 75% 15%, rgba(255, 120, 170, 0.14), transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(900px 650px at 50% 90%, rgba(120, 200, 255, 0.12), transparent 60%),
      #ffffff;
  }

  .wrap {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 20px 28px;
  }

  .hero {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .brand {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .mark {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(160, 120, 255, 0.9), rgba(255, 120, 170, 0.85));
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 44px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }

  .sub {
    margin: 6px 0 0;
    font-size: 16px;
    opacity: 0.75;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .nav {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    padding: 9px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .pill:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
  }

  .card {
    margin-top: 10px;
    padding: 18px 18px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .card h2 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .card ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 18px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .grid {
    margin-top: 18px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .tile {
    padding: 16px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .tile:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .tile h3 {
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .tile p {
    margin: 0;
    opacity: 0.78;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .foot {
    margin-top: 22px;
    padding-top: 14px;
    opacity: 0.65;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    h1 { font-size: 34px; }
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
